data.description: Extremely rare opportunity to own a home on one of Winston-Salem's most beautiful streets - a park-like setting! This 4 bedroom plus 3 bathroom home has an ideal floorplan, with primary and second bedrooms on the main floor, plus two more extra-large bedrooms on the upper level.  Current owners converted spacious walk-in closet into additional office space - but could easily be converted back. Owners also added a spacious screened porch off kitchen plus a stone patio. Fabulous backyard with two car garage and additional parking. Lower level has den/playroom, plus fantastic storage.  A true rarity in Buena Vista! Showings begin at noon on Friday 2/2. Occupancy early/mid April.
